title: Bobby And Dr. Oz Talk Coronavirus Safety + Is Mike D’s Girlfriend Coming To Nashville? + Raymundo’s Mom Makes Masks
itunes:title: Bobby And Dr. Oz Talk Coronavirus Safety + Is Mike D’s Girlfriend Coming To Nashville? + Raymundo’s Mom Makes Masks
description:
Bobby talks to Dr. Oz about common sense safety things related to the coronavirus pandemic. We get an update from Mike D. He asked his girlfriend to come quarantine together with him in Nashville. Raymundo’s mom calls the show to talk about masks. She's been busy making them and donating them to healthcare professionals and grocery store workers. Plus, Dustin Lynch tells us about quarantining with his girlfriend!
